\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"ef1e3309-ce4f-4603-930e-eb872634e5f7\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"820abced-8ac3-4707-b0d2-d5d646045d45\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T10:11:57.087662779Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"\"6E92ZMYYFZ\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"67c96682-916a-441b-85fa-b50724204384\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"113811cb-c611-41cc-b873-ab21bae7e2f3\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T10:12:39.966188352Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0"], "service_name": ["frontend", "productcatalogservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-04"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T10:10:24Z to 2025-06-20T10:30:24Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 10:10:24+00:00 to 2025-06-20 10:30:24+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的故障期间的异常指标数据，我将分析系统的根本故障原因，并提供关键的指标和影响实体。\n\n### 异常指标数据分析\n1. **TiDB 数据库异常**\n   - **指标名**: `failed_query_ops`, `duration_99th`, `store_unhealth_count`\n   - **组件**: `tidb-tidb`, `tidb-pd`\n   - **异常细节**: 查询失败次数急剧增加，95% 和 99%请求延迟显著上升，代表数据库的响应性能严重恶化。同时观察到 `store_unhealth_count` 从0上升至0.5，表明至少一个存储节点处于不健康状态。\n  \n2. **服务性能异常**\n   - **服务**: `checkoutservice`, `cartservice`, `frontend`\n   - **指标名**: `error_ratio`, `server_error_ratio`\n   - **异常细节**: 这些服务的错误率大幅提升，尤其是某些特定 Pod 如 `frontend-0` 的服务器错误率从0跃升至33.33。`checkoutservice-0` 和其他相关 Pod 的响应时间也大幅增加。\n\n3. **Pod 资源使用异常**\n   - **Pod**: `currencyservice-1`, `frontend-1`, `productcatalogservice-2`\n   - **指标名**: `pod_cpu_usage`\n   - **异常细节**: CPU 使用率在此期间增加，特别是在故障开始后急剧下降。\n\n### 结果发现\n结合故障期间的异常数据，我们可以看到，TiDB 数据库组件的查询失败、大量的请求延迟增强，以及服务组件如 `checkoutservice`、`cartservice` 和 `frontend` 出现高错误率。这些异常指标表明系统可能存在多个组件之间的高影响故障。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"failed_query_ops\",\n    \"duration_99th\",\n    \"store_unhealth_count\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failed query ops and high duration_99th indicate severe performance degradation in the database.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increased 'failed_query_ops' from 0.0 to 55.22, 'duration_99th' from 0.01 to 64.88.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"'server_error_ratio' sharply increased, indicating server-side issues leading to performance problems.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error ratio increased from 0.0 to 33.33.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage dropped unexpectedly, indicating possible resource allocation issues or pod instability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CPU usage fell from 0.05 to 0.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n这些初步发现需要进一步调查以确认每个组件的具体故障原因。这些分析将会为故障处理提供指导。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志信息，我进行了相应的分析。以下是分析结果和已识别的异常情况：\n\n### 关键日志信息\n- **错误类型**: `Region is unavailable`, `rpc error`\n- **服务名称**: `frontend`, `productcatalogservice`\n- **错误日志片段**:\n  - `\"error\":\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#PHOTO202): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"`\n  - `\"message\":\"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"`\n\n### 分析结果\n从日志中可以看到，问题主要集中在请求产品信息时发生了 \"Region is unavailable\" 的错误。多个服务在尝试访问产品信息时都遇到了这一点，尤其是 `frontend` 服务在请求推荐和检索产品时遭遇了此问题。\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"Error 9005\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"区域不可用导致服务无法检索产品信息\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志中多处报错显示区域不可用导致 rpc 错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析表明 `productcatalogservice` 是故障的关键组件，因为产品信息无法被查找，导致了服务的运行异常。进一步的调查可能需要更详细的网络或数据库层面的日志，以确定区域不可用的具体原因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据从链路追踪系统获取的数据以及调用链拓扑，我们可以分析到以下几点：\n\n### 检测到的延迟异常\n1. **ProductCatalogService 延迟**：\n   - `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 的调用在 `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice` 之间表现出显著延迟。\n   - 延迟从正常的9,500微秒增加到异常的39,333,334微秒。这表示延迟增加超过 4,000 倍。\n2. **CheckoutService 延迟**：\n   - `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder` 显示从正常的159,703微秒增加到异常的40,270,792微秒，延迟增加超过250倍。\n\n### 检测到的错误状态\n1. **ProductCatalogService 无效区域错误**：\n   - 错误代码：\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\" 在 `ProductCatalogService` 中频繁出现，尤其是在请求 `GetProduct` 接口时。这与数据存储相关系统的不可用有关，比如 TiDB。\n   \n2. **Frontend 和 CheckoutService 的前端 500 错误**：\n   - 许多 HTTP 500 错误出现在 `Frontend` 的接收操作中，特定请求获得了失败的订单准备错误提示。\n\n### 根因假设\n1. **TiDB 的 Region 不可用**：\n   - 由于 `ProductCatalogService` 的调用涉及从 TiDB 中获取产品信息，而遇到区域不可用的错误，这表明 TiDB 是此次故障的主要根因。\n\n2. **错误的级联效应**：\n   - 替代路径上 `Frontend` 和 `CheckoutService` 的 HTTP 500 错误可能是由于无法获取产品数据导致的连锁反应。\n\n下面是结构化的 JSON 输出：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->TiDB\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从9,500微秒到39,333,334微秒的增幅，和异常错误: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从159,703微秒到40,270,792微秒的延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"区域不可用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该分析强调了 ProductCatalogService 的调用依赖，以及 TiDB 中的区域问题影响了整体服务的正常运行。"}
